data.description: Opulent gated community with a Key West vibe in Paradise Preserve of Atlantic Beach community. This home backs up to Dutton Island Preserve separated by water the 2nd largest preserve in Jacksonville. No one will be building behind you. Fantastic natural lighting, and 20' ceilings. 2 Story home with the Owners Suite on the ground floor currently a 3 Bedroom that has an additional room upstairs that could be converted to a 4th Bedroom or reconverted for an indoor gym. 3 Full baths, Covered front porch & entry, Lanai is screened in with space for a summer kitchen. Fire pit and outdoor space with pavers. Plantation shutters throughout the main level except for 1 Guest Suite. LED lighting. Very open and inviting space. Pet friendly fenced yard.
